Their zeppoles are outstanding and their chicken rolls are just superb!!  Everytime my family and I go to Sunset, we always make it a point to grab a bite of the best slices in the 'hood!!   For those that complain that they take long ... remember ... YOU CAN'T RUSH PERFECTION!! For as long as they're open for business, we'll be sure to make the visit!!
